name: Air Transat A330-343X [C-GTSD] Close Up Landing at Vancouver Airport ᴴᴰ
description:
Another YVR video, this one featuring one of Air Transat's 4 A330-300s. In Calgary we only see their A330-200s, although there have been some equipment swaps lately (haven't caught any of them though), so this was pretty nice to see! I hope you enjoy this quick video.

Thanks for watching! Please comment, rate, and subscribe!
